{"id":232185496,"title":"請問各位有推薦的食物袋嗎？","content":"這幾天我白痴\n不小心弄丟了我媽的食物袋😭😭😭\n上網爬文找到個R牌 (沒業🙅🏻‍♀️)\n這家有人用過嗎？\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/GD03bou.jpg\n \n\n節目介紹也發現顏色頗好看的～\nhttp://bit.ly/2kCOtes\n\n自己平時需求是我媽規定我們每天都要吃足夠的水果\n所以每天都會幫我們姐妹準備三到五種水果都會洗好切好\n最一開始幾年用保鮮盒我覺得超佔空間\n後來買了食物袋覺得滿好清洗的\n吃完以後就可以收起來滿方便\n \n而且自從每天開始會用自備餐具後\n想到那些只用不到半小時就丟掉的塑膠餐具\n覺得以前真的很浪費.....\n尤其跟朋友去過幾次淨灘後更有感.......","excerpt":"這幾天我白痴，不小心弄丟了我媽的食物袋，上網爬文找到個R牌 （沒業‍️），這家有人用過嗎？節目介紹也發現顏色頗好看的～自己平時需求是我媽規定我們每天都要吃足夠的水果，所以每天都會幫我們姐妹準備三到五種","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-28T07:49:01.431Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-28T10:45:30.729Z","commentCount":8,"likeCount":65,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","愛地球","食物袋","不塑之客","無痕"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"中國文化大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":65}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03bou.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"865b6d0a-040b-4c07-a0b8-e7be8ca6f753","url":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03boul.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03boul.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03boul.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-28T07:49:01.431Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-28T10:45:30.729Z"},{"id":"865b6d0a-040b-4c07-a0b8-e7be8ca6f753","url":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03bou.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/GD03bou","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/GD03boul.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-28T07:49:01.431Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-28T10:45:30.729Z"}],"postAvatar":""}